    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一只蜜獾。🍯🦡 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是Bad。😈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲出去。潜进去。砸个痛快。偷个彻底。骑上所有能骑的。捉弄、挑衅、到处惹事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>做个Bad。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到开放动物园沙盒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲破你的围栏，在完全开放的动物园沙盒中释放混乱。探索新的动物围区，解锁那些令人愉快又邪恶的新挑战，把动物园变成一个混乱又疯狂的游乐场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1644050/extras/ca6e81b58f801e9a235305dbc1803a2a.avif?t=1762481397\" width=780 height=439 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BAD = 更棒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吓唬游客。捉弄无辜的动物。把饲养员逼疯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你越Bad，就能获得越多技能点。升级你的能力，解锁更多成为无法无天小麻烦的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1644050/extras/7cab2a258fe20ad99bc87733c3575cc1.avif?t=1762481397\" width=780 height=439 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超真实的蜜獾操作体验*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终于可以当Bad（一直做好事太无聊了）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破坏！！！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*操作其实没那么真实。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1644050/extras/b0ac73d85e068b76cc21107184e99ea6.poster.avif?t=1762481397\" width=780 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1644050/extras/b0ac73d85e068b76cc21107184e99ea6.webm?t=1762481397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个坏主意，大概都是个好主意！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你曾经想过：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和鳄鱼打架</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扔犀牛粪 💩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢一辆高尔夫球车</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让小孩哭</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这就是你的游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
